<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - পেজটি খুঁজে পাওয়া যায়নি</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans Bengali', sans-serif; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #374151; text-align: center; padding: 50px; }
        h1 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }
        p { font-size: 1.125rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        a { 
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        a:hover { background-color: #374151; }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Bengali:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>দুঃখিত, আপনি যে পেজটি খুঁজছেন তা খুঁজে পাওয়া যায়নি।</p>
    <a href="https://admission-calendar.com/">হোমপেজে ফিরে যান</a>
</body>
</html>